name: FVolumeControlStyle
doc: Represents the appearance of an SVolumeControl

SliderStyle: The style of the volume control slider
HighVolumeImage: Image to use when the volume is set to high
MidVolumeImage: Image to use when the volume is set to mid-range
LowVolumeImage: Image to use when the volume is set to low
NoVolumeImage: Image to use when the volume is set to off
MutedImage: Image to use when the volume is muted
